; Cmm_Commands/
;
; This directory contains Lauterbach PRACTICE (CMM) macro scripts used for
; individual debugger commands during test execution.
;
; Scripts in this directory are invoked from CANoe CAPL test cases via:
;   vFctn_T32_CommandCreate_Cmm_Commands(chCommand, "script_name.cmm")
;   lFctn_G_T32_RUN_CMM_CORE("Cmm_Commands\\script_name.cmm", core, timeout, params)
;
; Add project-specific CMM command scripts here as needed.
